Description.Details:
You take the datapad from [[SCN_MW,{SCN_MW.Callsign}]], "Give me the short version of what's on this datapad so that when I go over it later it all makes sense to me."

[[SCN_MW,{SCN_MW.Callsign}]] smiles and nods, "Aff, Commander.  The <i>short</i> story, as you have put it, is the easiest way to rebuild my <i>Minsk</i> is to obtain the OEM parts from their respective factories.  The time spent travelling to these systems will be offset by the time saved in assembling everything on a <i>Minsk MNK-102</i> donor chassis."

You nod, easily following along so far, "Please continue."

[[SCN_MW,{SCN_MW.Callsign}]] resumes {SCN_MW.Det} narrative, "We will need to travel to the following systems:

<color=#FFBF00><i>Novaya Zemlya for three components;

Galatea for three components;

Vipaava for two components;

Radstadt for one component;

Gibbs for one component;

Fletcher for one component</i></color>

The rest of the components needed are default systems on the <i>Minsk MNK-102</i>."

You mull over all of this info, "You mentioned seven star systems.  By my count, that is only six?"

[[SCN_MW,{SCN_MW.Callsign}]] nods again, "Aff, Commander.  The final destination is Rasalhague.  There we will find the facilty where we can assemble all the parts to create <i>Last Rites</i>."

You pat the datapad you are holding, "All of the pertinent details are in here then?  The items you are looking for, how we are supposed to get them and what not?  I do not want to find we are stealing or raiding a facility and starting something we cannot finish here."

[[SCN_MW,{SCN_MW.Callsign}]] stands up proudly in front of you, "Commander, on my honour as a clansman of the <i>Ghost Bear Dominion</i>, you can rest assured that everything I have outlined is above board."

You smile, "Thank you, MechWarrior.  I'll go over this with the rest of the Command Staff and see how best to approach your request.  I suspect this will be a very interesting series of events, and given your recorded exploits in, what was your mech called again... ah yes, <i>Last Rites</i>, {COMPANY.CompanyName} will garner even more lucrative contracts!"
